 The accident occurred between the Van Dyksdrift and Nelspruit offramps at around 21:10. According to the Middelburg SAPS, the BMW was from Maputo. It is unknown as to how many passengers it was carrying with the exception for the driver and one passenger.
The BMW passenger perished, but the two drivers involved both survived the collision. An investigation is underway to determine the cause of the accident.   Parents frustrated by a lack of space in Middelburg schools Traffic officers to appear in court for corruption #TrafficAlert: Two dead in Kranspoort accidents VIDEO: Two perish after truck jack-knifes • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za